overview: To find the world's hottest men and best performers, at KristenBjorn.com, we make casting videos in many different countries to see how well new candidates perform in front of a camera. These auditions are usually done between new candidates and experienced actors. Our website members ranked the ten scenes presented here as some of their favorites.
tagline: A cast of 21 of the world's hottest men
title: Kristen Bjorn's Casting Couch 3
